! Support for Node.js `v18` has ended
!
! Node.js `v18` reached its official End-of-Life (EOL) on `2025-04-30`. It no longer receives security updates, bug fixes, or support from the Node.js project and is no longer supported on Heroku.
!
! Suggestions:
! - Upgrade to a supported LTS version (20.x, 22.x, 24.x)
!
! https://devcenter.heroku.com/articles/nodejs-support#supported-node-js-versions
